Alia Bhatt: Death threat to Mahesh Bhatt, Alia Bhatt and family; filmmaker lodges police complaint 
2-3-2017 
Death threat to Mahesh Bhatt, Alia Bhatt and family; filmmaker lodges police complaint

Bollywood filmmaker Mahesh Bhatt has received a death threat from an unidentified caller who has demanded a sum of Rs 50 lakh to be deposited in a Lucknow-based bank branch. 
